@startuml
!include ../plantuml-theme.iuml
left to right direction

title 图 2.2 文档接入与处理用例图

actor "普通用户" as User

rectangle "文档接入与处理模块" {
  usecase "上传文档" as UC_Upload
  usecase "删除文档" as UC_Delete
  usecase "查询上传状态" as UC_UploadStatus
  usecase "查询处理状态" as UC_ProcessStatus
  usecase "分片上传与断点续传" as UC_Resume
  usecase "格式与内容校验" as UC_Validate
  usecase "完整性校验" as UC_Integrity
  usecase "异步入库" as UC_Ingest

  ' layout constraints: left column = user-triggered use cases
  UC_Upload -[hidden]down-> UC_Delete
  UC_Delete -[hidden]down-> UC_UploadStatus
  UC_UploadStatus -[hidden]down-> UC_ProcessStatus

  ' layout constraints: right column = included / triggered capabilities
  UC_Upload -[hidden]right-> UC_Validate
  UC_Validate -[hidden]down-> UC_Resume
  UC_Resume -[hidden]down-> UC_Integrity
  UC_Resume -[hidden]right-> UC_Ingest
}

User --> UC_Upload
User --> UC_Delete
User --> UC_UploadStatus
User --> UC_ProcessStatus

UC_Upload .> UC_Validate : <<include>>
UC_Upload .> UC_Resume : <<include>>
UC_Resume .> UC_Integrity : <<include>>
UC_Upload ..> UC_Ingest : <<触发>>

legend bottom
需求图只描述“用户可触发和可查询的能力”，
不在图中直接出现 Kafka、MinIO、向量库等实现组件。
endlegend
@enduml
